    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a mirror-like finish with no scratches, dents, or chips. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the upholstery is unmarked, and all electronic features and driver aids function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in peak performance, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. Every detail, from the engine bay to the undercarriage, has been kept in concours-level condition. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved with the utmost care.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
